Vector Subtraction:

Indha video la namma vector subtraction pathi paaka porom. Ippo enkitta rendu vector irukku, A and B. 
A vector oda value (4,2), B vector oda value (2,5). 
Indha rendu vector minus panni A − B oda resultant vector ah find panna porom.

Mudhala konjam vector addition concept ah nyabagam pannalaam, appo vector subtraction puriya easy ah irukkum.
Vector addition la, A vector oda x value um B vector oda x value um add pannuvom.
Adhe maari A vector oda y value um B vector oda y value um add pannuvom.
So, A + B na x direction la add pannuvom, y direction la add pannuvom. Ippadi add pannumbodhu namakku oru resultant vector kidaikkum.

Aana vector subtraction konjam different. Inga vector values mattum subtract panninaal pothaadhu, direction romba important. 
Ippo namma A − B find pannanum. Vector subtraction na enna na, A − B = A + (−B). Adhavadhu, 
Mudhala B vector oda opposite direction la oru vector create pannanum. Andha vector ah namma minus B nu solluvom.

Ippo indha concept ah visual ah RoboGebra use panni paakalam.
Ippo naan RoboGebra worksheet open pannuren. Inga note pannunga, indha worksheet la namma A, B nu use pannala; adhukku pathila u vector and v vector nu use pannirukkom. 
Concept same thaan, notation mattum different.

Mudhala u vector ah (4,2) nu set pannuren. Aprom v vector ah (2,5) nu set pannuren. Ippo marubadiyum nyabagam vachikkanum, u − v = u + (−v). 
So, first  u-v vector ah papom,  ithula v vector  reverse direction la move pannuren. 
Length same ah irukkum, aana direction mattum opposite ah maarum. Indha vector thaan −v vector.

Ippo namakku irukkura vectors u vector and  minus v vector. Ippo indha rendu vectora vector addition method use panni add pannalaam. 
Inga oru important rule irukku. Vector ah neenga enga naalum move pannalaam, aana length um direction um change pannakoodadhu, rotate um pannakoodadhu. 
Rotate pannama, length and direction change pannama, enga naalum move pannalaam.

Ippo u vector oda tip la  minus v vector oda tail ah vachikkiren. Aprom u vector oda tail la irundhu minus v vector oda tip varaikum oru vector draw pannuren. Indha vector thaan namakku kidaikkura u − v oda resultant vector. Andha resultant vector oda value (2, -3) nu RoboGebra la clear ah theriyum.

Ippo konjam compare pannina, vector addition la u vector oda tip la v vector oda tail vachchu resultant vector find pannuvom. 
Aana vector subtraction la u vector oda tip la minus v vector oda tail vachchu resultant vector find pannuvom. Difference romba simple. Addition la same direction vector use pannuvom, subtraction la opposite direction vector use pannuvom.
So  vector subtraction na opposite direction vector ah use panni pannura vector addition thaan. u − v = u + (−v) nu nyabagam vachikitta, 
vector subtraction romba easy ah visualize panni purinjikalaam, especially RoboGebra maadhiri tools use pannumbodhu.